- You're getting on my nerves.

780
01:16:17,635 --> 01:16:20,035
You'll be in jail again soon anyway.

781
01:16:21,035 --> 01:16:23,355
You mess things up
and are proud of it.

782
01:16:23,835 --> 01:16:25,155
That's enough ... - Shut up!

783
01:16:25,635 --> 01:16:26,955
Do you think I'm blind?

784
01:16:27,435 --> 01:16:30,715
That I don't know what
you're selling under the counter?

785
01:16:31,235 --> 01:16:35,715
People like you should be hanged!
- Pull yourself together!

786
01:16:38,235 --> 01:16:39,155
See you.

787
01:16:41,835 --> 01:16:45,475
I'd hang people like you.
A nice thick rope and that's that.

788
01:16:50,435 --> 01:16:52,355
Leave the shop in one piece.

789
01:17:23,035 --> 01:17:24,515
So, some tomato ...

790
01:17:26,355 --> 01:17:27,795
... that's always ...

791
01:17:28,275 --> 01:17:31,155
... very important,
tomato or peppers.

792
01:17:32,155 --> 01:17:33,115
Hello?

793
01:17:33,755 --> 01:17:35,195
Is anyone there?

794
01:17:37,915 --> 01:17:41,795
Good evening. Police. We've got
a search warrant for your shop.

795
01:17:42,915 --> 01:17:43,955
Are you the owner?

796
01:17:44,435 --> 01:17:46,115
I only help out.

797
01:18:05,675 --> 01:18:06,715
Bingo!

798
01:18:15,275 --> 01:18:17,435
Behind the counter!

799
01:19:07,275 --> 01:19:08,275
What's wrong?

800
01:19:08,755 --> 01:19:11,715
What's the time?
- Half past. Why?

801
01:19:12,195 --> 01:19:15,515
Martin had his test.
He was going to ring.

802
01:19:22,235 --> 01:19:23,715
Don't look like that.

803
01:19:24,715 --> 01:19:26,555
Why not? I'll look how I like.

804
01:19:27,035 --> 01:19:28,995
You're making a fool of yourself!

805
01:19:44,355 --> 01:19:45,115
Let me go.

806
01:19:50,075 --> 01:19:52,715
Hey! Are you crazy?
Open the door!

807
01:19:54,355 --> 01:19:55,755
Wolfgang, let me out!

808
01:19:57,355 --> 01:19:58,795
Are you mad?

809
01:20:00,475 --> 01:20:02,275
Open the door and let me out!

810
01:20:08,675 --> 01:20:10,115
Open the door!

811
01:20:15,675 --> 01:20:18,075
I want to see Manuela. - Sorry ...

812
01:20:18,555 --> 01:20:20,115
... but Manuela's at her mother's.

813
01:20:20,595 --> 01:20:22,235
And where's Rokko ?

814
01:20:22,715 --> 01:20:23,715
He's with her.

815
01:20:24,355 --> 01:20:26,915
What's going on?
I can hear Manuela.

816
01:20:29,835 --> 01:20:30,715
Go away!

817
01:20:32,875 --> 01:20:33,795
Manuela!

818
01:20:34,515 --> 01:20:36,275
Go or I'll call the police.

819
01:20:41,035 --> 01:20:46,355
Police? Leonhardt Frank Strasse.
We've got a burglar. Come quickly!

820
01:20:46,995 --> 01:20:48,115
My name is Riedel.

821
01:20:48,595 --> 01:20:51,155
Leonhard Frank Strasse in Pankow.

822
01:20:51,955 --> 01:20:53,715
There's only one of them .

823
01:21:00,635 --> 01:21:02,555
Open the door! Let me out!

824
01:21:05,115 --> 01:21:07,315
Are you mad? - The guy
outside's the problem.

825
01:21:07,795 --> 01:21:10,755
You're the problem!
- He'll break the windows!

826
01:21:11,835 --> 01:21:13,675
Martin! What's wrong?

827
01:21:14,155 --> 01:21:16,715
Wait. I'll get dressed
and come out.

828
01:21:19,835 --> 01:21:20,955
What's going on?

829
01:21:21,435 --> 01:21:23,835
Go to your room.
I'll tell you later.

830
01:21:25,075 --> 01:21:27,115
What's up? - I've got hassles,

831
01:21:27,595 --> 01:21:30,435
and I told you to go to
your room. - But what's wrong?

832
01:21:30,915 --> 01:21:31,835
Oh boy!

833
01:21:36,715 --> 01:21:37,635
Come here.

834
01:22:03,235 --> 01:22:04,155
Police!

835
01:22:05,235 --> 01:22:06,155
Police!

836
01:22:07,315 --> 01:22:08,875
Hands up! - Out of there!

837
01:22:10,835 --> 01:22:12,475
Hands up! I want your hands up!

838
01:22:14,035 --> 01:22:16,355
Come out! - I haven't
done anything!

839
01:22:18,435 --> 01:22:20,995
Both hands!
- I haven't done anything!

840
01:22:23,875 --> 01:22:28,835
Car calling HQ. - HQ here.
- Last name Schulz with a "z".

841
01:22:30,515 --> 01:22:32,795
Born 22.5.64 in Berlin.

842
01:22:33,995 --> 01:22:35,675
First name Martin.

843
01:22:36,155 --> 01:22:38,275
Don't worry. Everything's alright.

844
01:22:38,755 --> 01:22:41,795
But ... why are you here?
He hasn't done anything.

845
01:22:42,395 --> 01:22:45,075
Why did you ring us, then?

846
01:22:45,555 --> 01:22:46,475
I didn't.

847
01:22:47,275 --> 01:22:49,515
He is my husband. Let him out!

848
01:22:49,995 --> 01:22:53,195
Rolf? This looks like another
family drama. Let's go.

849
01:22:53,675 --> 01:22:58,035
Watch out! He's had a conviction
and he's wanted. Bring him in.

850
01:22:58,515 --> 01:23:00,635
What's wrong now? Open the door!

851
01:23:01,115 --> 01:23:03,315
Let him out! No, let me go!

852
01:23:05,115 --> 01:23:08,035
Are you mad or
something? - Go away!

853
01:23:09,115 --> 01:23:11,315
Martin, come out! Bloody pigs!

854
01:23:13,755 --> 01:23:14,595
Martin!

855
01:23:49,835 --> 01:23:51,475
Mr. Schulz,

856
01:23:53,035 --> 01:23:55,075
you've had a conviction for murder,

857
01:23:55,555 --> 01:23:58,915
after the reunification it was

858
01:23:59,395 --> 01:24:00,795
changed to manslaughter.

859
01:24:02,635 --> 01:24:06,995
When did you first go to prison?
- It's all in my file. I don't know ...

860
01:24:07,475 --> 01:24:08,835
Answer my question.

861
01:24:09,315 --> 01:24:10,515
When was it?

862
01:24:11,515 --> 01:24:16,835
It was before reunification. I was
sentenced in the summer of 1989 in Berlin.

863
01:24:17,315 --> 01:24:19,915
Manuela and I wanted to get out
of East Germany.

864
01:24:20,395 --> 01:24:23,955
East Germany was ... - You don't have
to tell me about East Germany.

865
01:24:24,475 --> 01:24:26,035
What had you done?

866
01:24:26,555 --> 01:24:30,195
I killed our house administrator, but
I didn't mean to, I flipped. It was a fluke.

867
01:24:30,675 --> 01:24:35,315
It says here You beat him
to death. Is that a fluke?

868
01:24:35,795 --> 01:24:41,035
The People's Police made the report ...
- The autopsy report confirms it.

869
01:24:41,555 --> 01:24:46,995
They did what they liked with people
who wanted to escape. You know that.

870
01:24:47,475 --> 01:24:50,555
I can see you were one of
them, too. - Don't get insolent!

871
01:24:53,115 --> 01:24:54,475
How do you know Victor Valentin?

872
01:24:55,915 --> 01:24:58,315
We were both in
Brandenburg Prison.

873
01:24:59,595 --> 01:25:01,475
Was he your friend? - My friend?

874
01:25:01,995 --> 01:25:04,915
Was there a sexual relationship?

875
01:25:06,115 --> 01:25:06,955
No.

876
01:25:08,115 --> 01:25:12,275
And you knew nothing about what
was sold under the counter?

877
01:25:12,755 --> 01:25:13,675
No.

878
01:25:14,955 --> 01:25:17,795
That was also a "fluke".
- I didn't do anything!

879
01:25:18,315 --> 01:25:20,315
Can you tell us where he is?

880
01:25:21,395 --> 01:25:22,755
No. - Mr. Schulz.

881
01:25:23,635 --> 01:25:28,875
I'll read you Section 184,
paragraph 4 of the Criminal Code.

882
01:25:29,355 --> 01:25:32,275
If the offender acts for
gain or as part of a group,

883
01:25:32,755 --> 01:25:37,875
the punishment is imprisonment
for a term of 6 months to 10 years,

884
01:25:38,355 --> 01:25:40,435
in addition to your probation.

885
01:25:40,955 --> 01:25:45,115
Are you scared of
Mr. Valentin's testimony?

886
01:25:45,595 --> 01:25:49,515
I didn't do anything! Where did
you learn these methods? In the Stasi?

887
01:25:51,075 --> 01:25:51,915
Listen here.

888
01:25:52,395 --> 01:25:53,675
There are places ...

889
01:25:54,155 --> 01:25:56,155
... where they hang
people like you.

890
01:26:00,115 --> 01:26:01,915
I know guys like you.

891
01:26:02,395 --> 01:26:04,115
I've met enough.

892
01:26:04,595 --> 01:26:09,355
Bit boring now, eh? No electric
shocks, no padded cells. What a shit!

893
01:26:09,835 --> 01:26:10,835
Mr. Schulz? - Yes?

894
01:26:11,875 --> 01:26:13,795
I'm not from the East.

895
01:26:14,395 --> 01:26:15,595
I'm from Bremen.

896
01:26:42,235 --> 01:26:44,075
I've brought you some things.

897
01:26:51,395 --> 01:26:52,475
Look.

898
01:27:02,675 --> 01:27:03,595
"Dear Dad,

899
01:27:05,195 --> 01:27:09,315
you have to jump over the snakes,
and watch out for the monkeys.

900
01:27:09,795 --> 01:27:11,395
Love from Rokko."

901
01:27:20,195 --> 01:27:22,315
It's not looking good.

902
01:27:25,595 --> 01:27:29,515
They want to get me with this.
I can't go through that again.

903
01:28:22,755 --> 01:28:25,555
Why did you get involved
with Victor Valentin?

904
01:28:26,035 --> 01:28:28,195
You knew he wasn't
good to be around.

905
01:28:28,675 --> 01:28:30,115
And the taxi license!

906
01:28:31,075 --> 01:28:34,875
I could have told you
you needed a special report.

907
01:28:35,435 --> 01:28:36,875
You can get the license,

908
01:28:37,355 --> 01:28:42,475
but only when you've settled
down, and another offence is unlikely.

909
01:28:42,915 --> 01:28:47,515
I can organize a special
report so you can take the test ...

910
01:28:47,995 --> 01:28:48,915
So?

911
01:28:49,555 --> 01:28:50,475
Martin...

912
01:28:51,035 --> 01:28:51,915
... old Eastie,

913
01:28:52,955 --> 01:28:55,155
did you think I'd leave
you in the lurch?

914
01:28:55,635 --> 01:28:57,195
I gave myself up.

915
01:28:59,435 --> 01:29:03,675
Do you think 5 years more or
less make any difference to me?

916
01:29:04,195 --> 01:29:06,635
Bring me my TV

917
01:29:07,155 --> 01:29:08,275
when you've time.

918
01:29:08,755 --> 01:29:10,755
And send my love to your wife.

919
01:29:11,235 --> 01:29:12,995
Don't think about...

920
01:29:13,475 --> 01:29:16,515
... what you shouldn't do, Martini.

921
01:29:16,995 --> 01:29:19,115
Think about what
you should do.

922
01:29:39,955 --> 01:29:41,875
So, here... and here.

